{"id":395,"ayahs":[{"number":78,"arabic":"قَالَ إِنَّمَآ أُوتِيتُهُۥ عَلَىٰ عِلْمٍ عِندِىٓ ۚ أَوَلَمْ يَعْلَمْ أَنَّ ٱللَّهَ قَدْ أَهْلَكَ مِن قَبْلِهِۦ مِنَ ٱلْقُرُونِ مَنْ هُوَ أَشَدُّ مِنْهُ قُوَّةًۭ وَأَكْثَرُ جَمْعًۭا ۚ وَلَا يُسْـَٔلُ عَن ذُنُوبِهِمُ ٱلْمُجْرِمُونَ","translation":"Answered he: “This [wealth] has been given to me only by virtue of the knowledge that is in me!” Did he not know that God had destroyed [the arrogant of] many a generation that preceded him - people who were greater than he in power, and richer in what they had amassed? But such as are lost in sin may not be asked about, their sins.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3330.mp3","surahId":28,"words":[{"id":63596,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"(ক্বারুণ) বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/028_078_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63597,"position":2,"arabic":"إِنَّمَآ","translation":"\"শুধুমাত্র","audioUrl":"wbw/028_078_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63598,"position":3,"arabic":"أُوتِيتُهُۥ","translation":"আমাকে দেয়া হয়েছে তা","audioUrl":"wbw/028_078_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63599,"position":4,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","translation":"এ কারণে যে","audioUrl":"wbw/028_078_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63600,"position":5,"arabic":"عِلْمٍ","translation":"জ্ঞান (রয়েছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/028_078_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63601,"position":6,"arabic":"عِندِىٓ ۚ","translation":"আমার নিকট\"","audioUrl":"wbw/028_078_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63603,"position":7,"arabic":"أَوَلَمْ","translation":"কি আর না","audioUrl":"wbw/028_078_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63604,"position":8,"arabic":"يَعْلَمْ","translation":"সে জানে","audioUrl":"wbw/028_078_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63605,"position":9,"arabic":"أَنَّ","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/028_078_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":63606,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/028_078_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},